  "description": "Traditional risotto has been given a Gousto makeover. We've swapped the traditional arborio rice for spelt, an ancient healthy wholewheat, which gives the risotto a coarse, nutty texture. We use half of the Italian hard cheese to form delicious cheese crisps which sit atop. ",
